Today we re announcing a major update to one of our most useful features: the Keyboard Extension. Here s what s new: A new and improved Keyboard Extension that allows you to translate while you type in apps like iMessage and WhatsApp Manage the keyboard s settings to switch autocorrect and auto caps on and off Copy and paste to translate any text in your conversation without leaving your messaging app Choose from 61 languages with custom keyboard layouts and tap to quickly switch between languages We re excited to see how these improvements help you take your translating to the next level. Make sure to rate and review iTranslate on the App Store so that we can keep breaking through language barriers together. HappyTranslating

Thanks for using iTranslate! We ve been working hard to make iTranslate even better and we re excited to announce this major app update. Here s what s new: Custom Phrasebook for you to collect and label all your most useful translations A redesigned even more user friendly interface Streamlined translation workflow with a new layout Enhanced language selection with improved language menus and intuitive navigation We hope these improvements will help you take your translating to the next level. Make sure to rate and review iTranslate on the App Store so that we can continue improving for you we really appreciate it! HappyTranslating

Behold iTranslate 15! This major update does not only include improved translations and bug fixes but also comes with an entirely fresh look for your favorite features! We completely reimagined our onboarding experience so you get the most out of iTranslate. New Lock Screen Widgets make it easier than ever to launch your favorite features directly from your iOS Lock Screen. For all soccer fans we are happy to introduce a new category in our Phrasebook so you never miss a translation during an important match. See for yourself and let us know what you think! HappyTranslating

Behold iTranslate 15! This major update does not only include improved translations and bug fixes but also comes with an entirely fresh look for your favorite features! Say Hello to our brand new Text Translation feature that now gives you an even better overview of every translation and the chosen languages! A warm welcome as well to our rejuvenated Voice Mode that makes real time conversation in foreign languages a piece of cake! And last but definitely not least we gaze upon the revamped Keyboard Extension which feels more native than ever and comes with full Chinese Pinyin support! See for yourself and let us know what you think! HappyTranslating

Introducing iTranslate for watchOS 2 and big update for iOS 9. This update brings you 2 major new improvements. A fully native App for watchOS 2 and a big update for iOS 9 with support for Split View Slide Over and Spotlight. WATCH OS 2 UPDATES: Fully native App built for watchOS 2. Uses watchOS 2 s built in voice recognition technology to instantly translate words phrases and text into more than 90 languages. Play back translations through the watch speaker no need to pull out your phone. Complications give you a quick and easy way to start a translation right from your Watch Face. It even automatically sets the language for you based on your current location. For example when you arrive in Berlin iTranslate for Apple watchOS 2 will know that the local language is German and set it accordingly. All you need to do is glance at your Apple Watch and tap a button to start a translation. Complications will automatically display common phrases like good morning and good evening on the watch face in the local language when you re abroad. The phrases are based on your location and the time of day. The new Time Travel feature lets you see phrases for a later time of day to make it easier to communicate for instance learn how to say good night in the local language before dinner so you re ready to say it when you leave. You can also see your recent translations by simply traveling back in time. iOS 9 UPDATES: Split View: Boost your productivity by putting iTranslate side by side with any App. iTranslate is the perfect companion App when you are working on a document in another language doing your Spanish homework or when you are simply browsing the web. The iTranslate User Interface automatically adapts perfectly to any size you set to ensure absolute flexibility. Thanks to Split View you now don t need to go back and forth all the time to do a simple translation making the iPad Air 2 and especially the new iPad Pro serious desktop replacements. Slide Over: In many cases you don t need iTranslate side by side but only for this one quick translation lookup. With Slide Over iTranslate is now just one swipe away. Whatever you are up to you can now bring up iTranslate with one simply swipe from the right side of your iPad Screen and you ll never be lost in translation again. The best thing: Slide Over will work on any iPad that supports iOS 9. Spotlight: Look up your recent translations trough Spotlight. Simply start typing and iTranslate will instantly show you recent translations right in Spotlight.

KEYBOARD EXTENSION Introducing iTranslate Keyboard. With our brand new and free Keyboard Extension you can now translate into over 90 languages in ANY App. Here are some possible scenarios: Chat with a Spanish girl right in WhatsApp Answer an Email in Chinese in the Mail App of your choice Post a tweet in French to impress your Twitter followers And did we already mention that it is completely free : GLANCE FOR APPLE WATCH For all you Apple Watch fans out there: iTranslate can now be accessed even faster with our brand new Glance for Apple Watch! HOUSECLEANING Besides the great new features above we also did some housecleaning check out our new Menu! as well as our usual round of bugfixes and performance improvements.
